✅ 1. LED Blink
ORG 0000H
START: MOV P1, #00H
LOOP: CPL P1.0
ACALL DELAY
SJMP LOOP

DELAY: MOV R2, #200
D1: MOV R1, #255
D2: DJNZ R1, D2
DJNZ R2, D1
RET
END

